OL,3,CThree people die in Listeria outbreak
OL,4,Clinked to desserts
OL,6,FThree people have died amid a listeria
OL,7,Foutbreak linked to desserts supplied
OL,8,Fto NHS hospitals and care homes from a
OL,9,Ffood manufacturer in Greater
OL,10,FManchester.
OL,12,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,13,Fconfirmed it has been investigating
OL,14,Ffive linked cases of listeria
OL,15,Finfection, which can cause vomiting,
OL,16,Fdiarrhoea, aches and pains and a high
OL,17,Ftemperature.
