OL,3,CThree people die in Listeria outbreak
OL,4,Clinked to desserts
OL,6,FAll five people suffered listeria
OL,7,Fbetween May and December last year,
OL,8,Fwith the UKHSA and the Food Standards
OL,9,FAgency (FSA) working to identify the
OL,10,Fcause.
OL,12,FOne of the people who died has had
OL,13,Ftheir death attributed to listeria.
OL,15,FThe other two were known to be
OL,16,Finfected with listeria at the time of
OL,17,Ftheir death.
