OL,3,CThree people die in Listeria outbreak
OL,4,Clinked to desserts
OL,6,FThe UKHSA has found a match for the
OL,7,Foutbreak strain in a chocolate and
OL,8,Fvanilla mousse and a strawberry and
OL,9,Fvanilla mousse made by Cool Delight
OL,10,FDesserts in Ramsbottom and supplied by
OL,11,FSusca Ltd in Hyde.
OL,13,FThe threshold of listeria found in the
OL,14,Fdesserts is known to be below the
OL,15,Flegal threshold of what healthy people
OL,16,Fcan tolerate.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
