OL,3,CThree people die in Listeria outbreak
OL,4,Clinked to desserts
OL,6,FHowever, because the dessert is
OL,7,Fsupplied to hospitals and care homes
OL,8,Fwhere vulnerable people are cared for
OL,9,Fand treated, a product recall has been
OL,10,Fissued.
OL,12,FThe manufacturer, Cool Delight
OL,13,FDesserts say they were unable to
OL,14,Fcomment at this stage.
OL,16,FDr Gauri Godbole, deputy director for
OL,17,Fgastrointestinal infections at UKHSA,
OL,18,Fsaid: "We are investigating a small
OL,19,Fnumber of cases of listeria.
