OL,3,CThree people die in Listeria outbreak
OL,4,Clinked to desserts
OL,6,F"The cause of the outbreak isn't
OL,7,Fconfirmed yet, however, our laboratory
OL,8,Ftesting has identified a potential
OL,9,Flink to a particular type of dessert,
OL,10,Fwhich is not available from retailers
OL,11,Fbut is served in some NHS trusts.
OL,13,F"Working with the Food Standards
OL,14,FAgency, on a precautionary basis, we
OL,15,Fhave advised NHS trusts and those
OL,16,Fproviding care to vulnerable people to
OL,17,Fstop serving these desserts while
OL,18,Finvestigations are under way.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
