OL,3,CThree people die in Listeria outbreak
OL,4,Clinked to desserts
OL,6,FInformation on the West Midlands Care
OL,7,FAssociation homepage said it had
OL,8,Freceived an FSA alert about Cool
OL,9,FDelight Desserts products for the
OL,10,Frecall of all ice cream, ice cream
OL,11,Frolls, mousses and yoghurts.
OL,13,FIt said these "products must all be
OL,14,Fwithdrawn from service, and placed in
OL,15,Fquarantine while investigations are
OL,16,Fongoing".
